@justinmk I tried the approach you shared, but when I checked the contents of the recorded register it didn't have the pasted content. When I checked the contents of the register that I was recording in, in `vim.paste` it still had the content from the previous recording. 
I also tried using `nvim_feedkeys` instead of `nvim_put` to simulate the contents being typed thinking it would solve this but it didn't work either.
Do you (or anyone else) have any suggestions on how to resolve this?
